Package: jaid
Title: Joo's Functional Aid Toolkit
Version: 0.0.0.9002
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Seokhoon", family = "Joo", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "seokhoonj@gmail.com")
Description: High-performance utilities for efficient and productive programming, 
    including vector and matrix helpers, data.table-friendly in-place transformations, 
    string tools for Japanese text (e.g., Zenkaku to Hankaku), convenient I/O wrappers, 
    and date/time helpers. Selected routines are implemented in C for speed.
